Luke leads the data and analytics product strategy and delivery across AGL's Customer Experience transformation program. This includes;

The management of internal and customer facing data products across the Service Design & Delivery Framework (SDDF);

Day-to-day leadership of Data Product Owners whom are creating the building blocks for AGL's next best action and customer personalisation strategies;

Acting as the business partner to business units across Digital Strategy and Operations, Sales & Marketing, Customer Operations and Energy Trading; and

Influencing AGL's big-data and cloud data platform strategies based on the data and analytical needs of the the end customer and/or business unit.

